#: ../../source/opac.rst:235
msgid "|image957|"
msgstr "|image957|"

#: ../../source/opac.rst:237
msgid ""
"And finally if you have enabled FRBR and you have other editions of the "
"title in your collection you will see the 'Editions' tab."
